l]], graduating in 2018.<ref name=\"herald big break\" />\n\n==Filmography==\n=== Film ===\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes<ref name=\"imbd\">{{Cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm5057169/|title=Thomasin McKenzie|website=IMDb|access-date=2018-06-30}}</ref>\n|-\n|2012\n|''Existence''\n|Scraps\n|\n|-\n|2014\n|''Consent: The Louise Nicholas Story''\n| Young Louise \n|\n|-\n|2014\n|''A Long Beside''\n| Kate (young)\n|Short film\n|-\n| 2014\n| ''[[The Hobbit: The Battle of the Five Armies]]''\n| Astrid\n| \n|-\n| 2015\n| ''The Boyfriend Game''\n| Edith\n|\n|-\n| 2017\n| ''[[The Changeover#Film Adaptation|The Changeover]]''\n| Rose Keaton\n|\n|-\n| 2018\n| ''[[Leave No Trace (film)|Leave No Trace]]''\n| Tom\n|[[National Board of Review Award for Breakthrough Performance]]<br /> [[San Diego Film Critics Society]] Award for Best Breakthrough Performance <br /> Nominated - [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Young Performer|Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Young Actor/Actress]] <br /> Nominated - [[Detroit Film Critics Society Award for Best Supporting Actress]] <br /> Nominated - [[Gotham Independent Film Award for Breakthrough Actor]] <br /> Nominated - [[Independent Spirit Award for Best Supporting Female]]\n|-\n| rowspan=3 | 2019\n| ''[[The King (2019 film)|The King]]''\n| [[Philippa of England|Queen Philippa of Denmark]]\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Jojo Rabbit]]''\n| Elsa Korr\n|Nominated - [[Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Young Performer|Critics' Choice Movie Award for Best Young Actor/Actress]]\n|-\n| ''[[True History of the Kelly Gang (film)|True History of the Kelly Gang]]''\n| Mary\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=2|2020\n| ''[[Lost Girls (film)|Lost Girls]]''\n| Sherre Gilbert\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Last Night in Soho]]''\n| Eloise\n| Post-production\n|-\n|2021\n| ''The Justice of the Bunny King''\n|\n|Post-production\n|-\n| 2021\n| ''[[The Power of the Dog (film)|The Power of the Dog]]''\n|\n| Filming\n|}\n\n=== Televisi