com/live Watch Live]\n| online serv 2  = \n| online chan 2  = \n}}\n'''Amrita TV''' (Malayalam: \u0d05\u0d2e\u0d43\u0d24 \u0d1f\u0d3f.\u0d35\u0d3f.), was launched in 2005, as a 24-hour Malayalam, general entertainment satellite channel.\n\n==Theme Song==\nThe theme song, \"Lokasamastha,\" was composed by [[Rahulraj]] for [[Mata Amritanandamayi]]'s 50th birthday celebrations in 2003 and later taken as the theme of Amrita TV.\n\n==Current shows==\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Title !! Time slot !!Notes!!Year!!Category\n|-\n|Sandhya Deepam||6:25 pm IST(DAILY)||Hosted By Romy Sreekumar ||2005\u2013Present||Devotional Show\n|-\n|Sreshthabharatham||7:00pm IST(Mon-Fri)||Hosted by [[Nithya Das]]||2018- present||Reality Show\n|-\n|Ayyappa Saranam||7:30pm IST(Mon-Fri)||Kaushik Babu , ||2019-Present||serial\n|-\n\n|Kerala Dance League||8:00 pm IST (Mon-Fri)||[[Kaniha|Kanika]], Sreejith Master, [[Bharath (actor)|Bharath]]||2019-Present||Reality Show\n|-\n|Jananayakan||8:00 pm IST (Sat-Sun)||[[Renji Panicker]] , [[Shaji Kailas]]||2019-Present||Talk show\n|-\n|Thonnyaksharangal||9:00 pm IST(Monday to Friday )||Marsheena Neenu,Kavitha Nair, Yedhukrishnan||2019\u2013Present||Serial\n|-\n|Just for fun :Chumma 2||9:00 pm IST (Fri-Sun)||Vimal Pillai,Hrishikesh,Veena Bharath,Kshama Krishnan||2019-Present||Serial\n|-\n|Kadhayallithu Jeevitham||9:30 pm IST(Monday to Friday)||Hosted By [[Vidhubala]]|| 2010\u2013Present||Family show\n|-\n|Annies Kitchen||6:55 pm IST (Sat-Sun)||Hosted By [[Annie (actress)|Chitra Shaji kailas]]|| 2015\u2013Present ||Cookery show\n|-\n|the global indian||10:30 pm IST(Sunday)||rowspan=4 {{N/A}} ||2018-Present||\n|-\n|Nadakame Ulakam||10:30 pm IST(SATURDAY) ||2010\u2013Present||Political Satire\n|-\n|People's Choice||10:30 am IST(SUNDAY)|| 2016\u2013Present||Politics\n|-\n|TOP 10 @10 ||10:00pm IST(Daily)||  2004\u2013Present||NEWS\n|-\n|Malayali Durbar||8:00pm IST(SAT-SUN)||Hosted By [[Tini Tom]]||2014\u2013Present||Talk Show\n|-\n|Arogyavartha||12:30 Noon IST